s-against-gaza/2014/07/08/ | title = IDF’s Operation "Protective Edge" Begins Against Gaza | publisher = Jewish Press | accessdate = 8 July 2014 | archive-date = 2014-07-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140710004714/http://www.jewishpress.com/news/breaking-news/idfs-operation-protective-edge-begins-against-gaza/2014/07/08/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。哈马斯成员绑架并杀害三名以色列青少年后，以色列国防军逮捕了激进分子领导人，哈马斯隨後朝以色列发射火箭弹，为期七周的冲突由此爆發。以色列的空袭和轰炸以及巴勒斯坦的火箭彈袭击共造成数千人死亡，其中绝大多数是加沙人。 <ref name=voa_thousands_flee>[http://www.voanews.com/content/israel-makes-first-ground-incursion-in-gaza/1956454.html ''Thousands Flee Gaza Homes Under Israel Threat''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/israel-makes-first-ground-incursion-in-gaza/1956454.html |date=20140723182037 }}. Voice of America, 13 July 2014</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Zonszein|first=Mairav|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/27/israel-kills-more-palestinians-2014-than-any-other-year-since-1967|title=Israel killed more Palestinians in 2014 than in any other year since 1967|date=2015-03-27|work=The Guardian|access-date=2020-03-03|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412025048/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/27/israel-kills-more-palestinians-2014-than-any-other-year-since-1967}}</ref><ref name="OCHA">{{cite web |url=http://www.ochaopt.org/documents/ocha_opt_sitrep_04_09_2014.pdf |title=Occupied Palestinian Territory: Gaza Emergency |format=PDF |date=4 September 2014 |accessdate=4 September 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913014525/http://www.ochaopt.org/documents/ocha_opt_sitrep_04_09_2014.pdf |archivedate=2014年9月13日 }}</ref><ref name="ministry">{{cite web|url=http://www.imemc.org/article/68969|title=Ministry of Health: "2145 Palestinians, Including 578, Killed In Israel's Aggression"|accessdate=30 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626174848/http://www.imemc.org/article/68969|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

衝突開始50天後，以色列與巴勒斯坦武裝組織哈馬斯同意埃及提出的方案，自格林威治時間8月26日16時起在加沙實施無限期停火，為50以天來造成超過2,100多人死亡的加薩戰事畫下句點。<ref name="WJ-巴以長期停火">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldjournal.com/view/full_van/25676566/article-%E4%BB%A5%E5%B7%B4%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-7%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%A |title=以巴無限期停火 7年加薩封鎖解除 |publisher=世界新聞網 |date=2014-08-27 |accessdate=2014-08-28 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>停火協議生效後，以軍機飛離加沙上空，加沙武裝人員也停止向以色列境內發射火箭彈，以色列同時開放以色列與加薩間的邊界關卡，讓人道援助和賑濟物資和重建材料迅速進入，解除2007年以來對加沙走廊的封鎖。<ref name="WJ-巴以長期停火" />

