{{main|2014年以色列青少年绑架谋杀案}}
三名以色列青少年2014年6月于[[约旦河|约旦河]]西岸遭到绑架后遇害的一连串事件，引发了此次行动，以色列指责哈马斯犯下此罪行。以色列国防军声称两名绑架青少年的犯罪嫌疑人，为哈马斯的部下<ref name="CBS 2014 Jun 26">{{Citation | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/israel-ids-2-main-suspects-in-teens-disappearance/ | title = Israel IDs 2 main suspects in teens disappearance | newspaper = [[CBS_News|CBS News]] | date = 26 June 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201114235007/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/israel-ids-2-main-suspects-in-teens-disappearance/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | title = Operation Brother’s keeper | contribution = In extended version of kidnapped teens call to police, murderers heard singing in celebration | contribution-url = http://www.jpost.com/Operation-Brothers-Keeper/In-extended-version-of-kidnapped-teens-call-to-police-murderers-heard-singing-in-celebration-361270 | newspaper = [[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]] | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127043956/https://www.jpost.com/Operation-Brothers-Keeper/In-extended-version-of-kidnapped-teens-call-to-police-murderers-heard-singing-in-celebration-361270 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但以色列当局没能给出证据<ref name=Islamist_group_blame>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/israel/10901225/Hamas-kidnapping-Islamist-group-to-blame-for-youths-kidnapping-Benjamin-Netanyahu-says.html ''Hamas kidnapping: Islamist group to blame for youths' 'kidnapping', Benjamin Netanyahu says''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/israel/10901225/Hamas-kidnapping-Islamist-group-to-blame-for-youths-kidnapping-Benjamin-Netanyahu-says.html |date=20201128113215 }}. Robert Tait, The Telegraph, 15 June 2014</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/07/hamas-didnt-kidnap-the-israeli-teens-after-all.html |title=It Turns Out Hamas May Not Have Kidnapped and Killed the 3 Israeli Teens After All |accessdate=2014-07-26 |archive-date=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730074250/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/07/hamas-didnt-kidnap-the-israeli-teens-after-all.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>），哈马斯否认参与事件，对事件亦不知情<ref name=Newman>[http://www.timesofisrael.com/netanyahu-hamas-behind-kidnapping-of-three-teenagers/#ixzz35Dg026iL ''Netanyahu: Hamas behind kidnapping of three teenagers''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/netanyahu-hamas-behind-kidnapping-of-three-teenagers/#ixzz35Dg026iL |date=20201112003950 }}. Marissa Newman, The Times of Israel, 15 June 2014</ref>。以色列军队在冲突中擊斃的10名巴勒斯坦人含两名未满18岁的巴勒斯坦青年<ref>{{Citation | title = Middle East & Africa: Murder of three kidnapped Israeli youths has set dangerous new spate | url = http://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21606288-murder-three-kidnapped-israeli-youths-has-set-dangerous-new-spate | newspaper = The Economist | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2018-03-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180330193436/https://www.economist.com/news/middle-east-and-africa/21606288-murder-three-kidnapped-israeli-youths-has-set-dangerous-new-spate | dead-url = no }}</ref>，逮捕数百名在西岸寻找失踪少年的人，并发动“兄弟的老板行动”，摧毁哈马斯的基础设施和监狱<ref>{{Citation | first = Yoav | last = Zitun | url = http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4532764,00.html | title = Rescue units rushed to Hebron, searching wells and caves | publisher = [[Ynet|Ynet]] | date = 21 June 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127081632/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4532764,00.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref>{{Citation | first = John B | last = Judis | url = http://www.newrepublic.com/article/118630/israel-palestine-murders-cause-criss-will-john-kerry-step | title = John Kerry's First Peace Effort in Israel and Palestine Failed, But Now He Needs to Try Again | newspaper = [[The_New_Republic|The New Republic]] | date = 9 July 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201107133857/https://newrepublic.com/article/118630/israel-palestine-murders-cause-criss-will-john-kerry-step | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在搜寻三名失踪的以色列青少年期间，以色列国防军逮捕了多名被释放用以交换[[吉拉德·沙利特|吉拉德·沙利特]]的战俘。自从2012年11月[[云柱行动|云柱行动]]达成停火协议，哈马斯已被视为从加薩地带发射火箭弹的武装分子，对2014年7月8日向以色列发射火箭弹幕一事有直接责任<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2014/0707/Ending-detente-Hamas-takes-responsibility-for-today-s-spike-in-rocket-fire-video | title=Ending détente, Hamas takes responsibility for today's spike in rocket fire (+video) | work=The Christian Science Monitor | accessdate=11 July 2014 | last=Bryant | first=Christa Case | archive-date=2017-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707114455/https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2014/0707/Ending-detente-Hamas-takes-responsibility-for-today-s-spike-in-rocket-fire-video | dead-url=no }}</ref>，并坚持再次以释放被捕者作为停火条件<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/for-israel-in-gaza-a-delicate-balancing-act/ | title=For Israel in Gaza, a delicate balancing act | work=The Times of Israel | accessdate=8 July 2014 | archive-date=2020-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728053109/https://www.timesofisrael.com/for-israel-in-gaza-a-delicate-balancing-act/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

三名遇害以色列人的葬礼几小时后，名为穆罕默德·阿布·哈德尔的16岁[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]少年遭绑架，并被[[犹太教|犹太教]]极端分子进行报复性攻击活活杀死<ref name="Sterman">{{cite news | first =Adiv | last =Sterman | title =Six Jewish extremists arrested in killing of Jerusalem teen | work =The Times of Israel | url =http://www.timesofisrael.com/suspects-arrested-in-killing-of-east-jerusalem-teen/ | date =6 July 2014 | accessdate =10 July 2014 | archive-date =2020-11-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003448/https://www.timesofisrael.com/suspects-arrested-in-killing-of-east-jerusalem-teen/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>。六名涉嫌谋杀罪的犹太犯罪嫌疑人已被以色列警方逮捕<ref name="Sterman" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.maannews.net/eng/ViewDetails.aspx?ID=710388 |title=Israel arrests suspects in murder of Palestinian teen |publisher=[[Ma'an_News_Agency|Ma'an News Agency]] |date=6 July 2014 |accessdate=July 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714222658/http://www.maannews.net/eng/ViewDetails.aspx?ID=710388 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。哈德尔的尸体被发现，导致[[东耶路撒冷|东耶路撒冷]]的抗议和骚乱，蔓延至全国各地的阿拉伯人村庄<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/spate-of-riots-erupt-in-northern-israel/|title=Protests erupt again in East Jerusalem, southern Israel|date=6 July 2014|accessdate=10 July 2014|work=The Times of Israel|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234040/https://www.timesofisrael.com/spate-of-riots-erupt-in-northern-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以色列总理[[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]正式提出慰问和道歉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/07/world/meast/mideast-tensions/|title=Israel calls up reservists as rockets fly|date=8 July 2014|accessdate=11 July 2014|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128004132/https://edition.cnn.com/2014/07/07/world/meast/mideast-tensions/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，加薩向以色列发射火箭弹，导致以色列向加薩地带发动空袭。潜在的休战被埃及撮合，哈马斯同意拿以色列承诺停止空袭为条件，停止发射火箭弹，据报道该交易于7月4日达成。哈马斯透露休战议定将在数小时内宣布。以色列一名发言人表示：“一切在哈马斯的法庭里<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28156268 | title = Hamas 'ready for Gaza ceasefire' if Israeli raids stop | newspaper = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | date = 4 July 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024639/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28156268 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”

然而公告迟迟没来。7月7日，以色列袭击了[[加薩|加薩]]几处地点，包括[[贝尔谢巴|贝尔谢巴]]、[[阿什杜德|阿什杜德]]、[[奥法基姆|奥法基姆]]、[[亚实基伦|亚实基伦]]和[[內提沃特|內提沃特]]，加薩随即向以色列境内发射100枚火箭予以还击<ref>{{Citation | url = http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/7/7/israel-launched-deadlyairstrikesingaza.html | title = Israel launches military offensive in Gaza | publisher = [[Al-Jazeera|Al-Jazeera]] | date = 7 July 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2014-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140709041844/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/7/7/israel-launched-deadlyairstrikesingaza.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref>{{Citation | first = Noam | last = Sheizaf | url = http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/7/8/israeli-palestinianclashesupsettingisraelifaithinstatusquo.html | title = Israeli-Palestinian clashes upsetting Israeli faith in status quo | publisher = [[Al-Jazeera|Al-Jazeera]] | date = 7 July 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2014-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140711193837/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2014/7/8/israeli-palestinianclashesupsettingisraelifaithinstatusquo.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/1.603472 | type = live updates | date = 7 July 2014 | title = Rockets bombard south, Hamas claims responsibility | work = [[Haaretz|Haaretz]] | accessdate = 11 July 2014 | archive-date = 2015-07-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150726021530/http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/1.603472 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。周一晚，以色列打击了加薩地带的50个目标<ref>{{Citation | first1 = Spencer | last1 = Ho | first2 = Yifa | last2 = Yaakov | url = http://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-pounds-dozens-of-gaza-targets-in-major-counteroffensive/ | title = Israel hits Hamas, Islamic Jihad leaders after rockets land north of Tel Aviv | type = blog | at = 08:02 | newspaper = [[The_Times_of_Israel|The Times of Israel]] | date = 8 July 2014 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | archive-date = 2020-11-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126204736/https://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-pounds-dozens-of-gaza-targets-in-major-counteroffensive/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，加薩的巴勒斯坦武装分子在周二7月8日，24小时内以色列发射超过140枚火箭弹，北至[[哈代拉|哈代拉]]超越[[特拉维夫|特拉维夫]]，以色列反火箭弹防御系统铁穹拦截30枚。以色列还挫败了武装分子从海岸进行的渗透<ref>{{cite web |last= Horovitz |first= David |url= http://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-pounds-dozens-of-gaza-targets-in-major-counteroffensive |title= Israel hits Hamas, Islamic Jihad leaders after rockets land north of Tel Aviv |work= The Times of Israel |date= 23 December 2013 |accessdate= 10 July 2014 |archive-date= 2020-11-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201126204736/https://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-pounds-dozens-of-gaza-targets-in-major-counteroffensive/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>，并于周二上午开始主要军事行动。

以色列国防军发言人在行动开始前发布推特，声称“以色列国防军已在加薩走廊开展对抗[[哈马斯|哈马斯]]的保护边缘行动，以阻止以色列公民每天都面对的恐怖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4539234,00.html | title = IDF launches Gaza operation 'against Hamas' following massive rocket barrage on south | work = [[Ynetnews|Ynetnews]] | accessdate = 8 July 2014 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112040329/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4539234,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.jta.org/2014/07/07/news-opinion/israel-middle-east/israel-planning-to-escalate-gaza-strikes-as-rocket-attacks-increase | title=Israel launches operation to stop Gaza-based rocket fire | publisher=[[Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency|Jewish Telegraphic Agency]] | accessdate=8 July 2014 | archive-date=2018-08-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815030511/https://www.jta.org/2014/07/07/news-opinion/israel-middle-east/israel-planning-to-escalate-gaza-strikes-as-rocket-attacks-increase | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

巴勒斯坦总统发言人表示，此次行动是“对巴勒斯坦人宣战”，并抗议以方声称的屠杀无辜，还称“巴勒斯坦必将以一切合法手段保卫自己的权利<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.maannews.net/eng/ViewDetails.aspx?ID=711019 | title = Presidency: Palestinians have the right to defend themselves | publisher = [[Ma'an_News_Agency|Ma'an News Agency]] | date = 8 July 2014 | access-date = 2014-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714213747/http://www.maannews.net/eng/ViewDetails.aspx?ID=711019 | archive-date = 2014-07-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>”。

保护边缘行动是加薩自2008-2009年[[加薩战争|加薩战争]]以来最为致命的军事行动<ref name="Middle East Eye">{{cite web | url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/20-palestinians-killed-overnight-un-holds-emergency-talks-980381607 | title=20 Palestinians killed overnight as UN holds emergency talks | publisher=Middle East Eye | accessdate=10 July 2014 | archive-date=2018-11-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122140552/https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/20-palestinians-killed-overnight-un-holds-emergency-talks-980381607 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 行动目的 ==
以色列方面的目的是消除以色列南部遭火箭弹袭击的威胁，并摧毁哈马斯的武器储存设施及其他针对以色列军事行动的基础设施，削弱哈马斯的军事能力。<ref>[http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-07/08/c_1111518733.htm 以色列空袭加沙南部 造成4人死亡15人受伤] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-07/08/c_1111518733.htm |date=20190912015951 }}，2014年7月8日。</ref>

